"""
TradingAI Pro v2.0 — Comprehensive Discord Trading Bot
=======================================================

Full-featured Discord bot with 40+ slash commands, auto channel setup,
interactive embeds, buttons, and market data across US/HK/JP/Crypto.

Features:
  • Auto-create organized channels on guild join
  • Welcome onboarding embed with guided setup
  • 40+ slash commands grouped by category
  • Real-time stock data via yfinance
  • AI analysis, scoring, and recommendations
  • Position sizing / risk management calculator
  • Multi-market: US, HK, JP, Crypto
  • Portfolio dashboard (paper trading)
  • Price alert system
  • Push methods for signals, reports, alerts
"""

import asyncio
